{"tid":316752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法律意見：可由人大重劃香港邊界解高鐵爭議","createTime":"2017-07-11T03:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T12:21:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc09556663c8ec80af77389d4b2f6358fec8fb27","tid":316752,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170711/s00001/d9575f8afdb08b742dfd4db86b2ce01e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2Fd9575f8afdb08b742dfd4db86b2ce01e.jpg&h=e6d12535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段「一地兩檢」方案暫未出爐，但有報道引述消息指，兩地已就「一地兩檢」達共識，在高鐵西九龍總站內劃出內地管轄專區，全面行使內地司法管轄權。報道又引述法律界人士建議，可「由人大常委會重劃香港特區的邊界」，以解決法律問題。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道，港府已同意在高鐵西九龍總站內劃出內地管轄專區，規定香港法律在專區內並不適用，交由內地管轄，而有關專區包括西九龍總站內的內地出入境管制區、月台及車廂，香港境內高鐵沿線路軌則仍由香港法律管轄。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有關安排將 會由「雙邊立法」實施，即由本港立法會及人大常委會分別進行立法。<br />\n<br />\n至於有質疑把香港部分分割出來受制內地法律司法管轄權，並不附合《基本法》，報道引述法律界人士建議，可「由人大常委會重劃香港特區的邊界，將高鐵站內的內地管轄專區劃出香港特區的邊界之外」，即不用實施香港法律。<br />\n<br />\n報道另引述全國政協常委唐英年指，「一地兩檢」與高鐵不可分割，直言「如果兩地兩檢，不如唔好做高鐵」。他又呼籲市民相信政府。"},{"pid":"b2ddadacb8a225a98c67b4208aa36c122ed86dcf","tid":316752,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499737424397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499737424397&d=4OnnOyGQHbV%2FZoZkzvCjljQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bc8f1919\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170711%2Fs00001%2F1499737424397&h=4e5dae58\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170711/s00001/1499737424397</a>"},{"pid":"f49f71f8ca345e14e7d15b045a119e0b7a559b42","tid":316752,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"一國一制算鳩數啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7797fbefde8f42d20665dc32c5174d593401861","tid":316752,"uid":121844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"劃曬成個香港做深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071d11db0faa30b70fdf799f611843c7d9c7eaf7","tid":316752,"uid":79410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:27:59.000Z","msg":"起之前, 已經話左冇可能一地兩檢.<br />\n政府死都話要起, 起左後就搞掂.<br />\n搞掂既方法,原來就係割地.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894c906d88293fb4b9c98358d1da899772488fb5","tid":316752,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"我做我大事　我話我話事<br />\n隨時能翻天覆雨一次　風聲吹過我先知"},{"pid":"bdb2515be8c937072b160c8ad09de5513477ea3b","tid":316752,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"原來解決方法就係支那話乜就乜<br />\n食屎口廿"},{"pid":"b1ef90308ce58bf46e8737574fd4406b4d046d7b","tid":316752,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"廣東省香港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1538c209f78b958e3d13dee8e9eb3cf50eebd1e2","tid":316752,"uid":20867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"今日割五城 明日割十城"},{"pid":"91f4e83a29fe8f4a3ac7c104874111dfcf931c48","tid":316752,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"唔怪得呢排死嘈，話中英聯合聲會過期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來要直接割裂香港，將西九地區，直接廢除基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adba0a973a83a4f22cee2529f6187dc6862baf3","tid":316752,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"九龍半島及新界永久割讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/