r />\n講o既人居心叵測</blockquote><br />\n又要想基本法借香港過橋扮兩制呃外資值但又想完全控制<br />\n食屎啦支那<br />\n不如廢左一國兩制佢<br />\n到時睇下你堆支那人民廢紙有冇人要？"},{"pid":"a03e51274d16c8b20f8902ce89eb5c050a2a353d","tid":316752,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廣東省香港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳市香港區</blockquote><br />\n深圳市羅湖區香港街道辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb46d7694deef6d4509bb3b7f946a2fabbb7fc30","tid":316752,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日割五城 明日割十城</blockquote><br />\n二十年前已經割半個後海灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee96dac6b0547467a93fda36610a64d395a9f57","tid":316752,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>割都未係最大問題<br />\n最大問題係又搵人大干預<br />\n等同主動放棄自治權<br />\n仲要係為咗繞過基本法<br />\n講o既人居心叵測</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢用淫大去攪基本法，迫香港法院硬食（同上次宣誓單野一樣）。<br />\n<br />\n但今次變相將ＨＫＳＡＲ地域割裂，應該同中英聯合聲明有衝突（令西九部份地區冇基本法保護，失去五十年不變承諾）。<br />\n<br />\n英國應該有理據屌佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ecd36b4cd347e2a89d4e1ac3812adb45f64383","tid":316752,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e472e36dc985aeaf054f884dfecbef4247033c05","tid":316752,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係又釋法</blockquote><br />\n而家佢唔係要釋法, 佢係要修改.</blockquote><br />\n索性建議美國取消香港政策"},{"pid":"79170eec412e27fd4e56eba5b0239c15181236ad","tid":316752,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"大富翁任揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次要埋中環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00426059163596636ae80a896769e605bf188455","tid":316752,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"682bbed2e0c91800331be7f909ff3dd70ca638ad","tid":316752,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"索性廢除一國兩制一了百了啦屌"},{"pid":"723d452e79ee736b877f8fa51094e8ea5af318d8","tid":316752,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索性廢除一國兩制一了百了啦屌</blockquote><br />\n人大可重劃一國兩制範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d6810e9d49deca99888dbb789b0c72480459ab","tid":316752,"uid":99872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"由個仆街董收order推所謂的高官問責制已知死得，就係知比你地公務員做阿頭點會過到呢d政策，緊係搵自己隻狗做啦，而家鍾意點就點，割地？easy"},{"pid":"38e7c751c14cead3b0e8014aa2ee20dd7b6f063d","tid":316752,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>林鄭拒證實是否已就一地兩檢達共識<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，政府與內地已就高鐵一地兩檢方案達成共識，會將西九站、月台及車廂劃為內地管轄區，林鄭月娥不願證實報道，表示希望有全面方案再作解說。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"efe0c0a518b8ed31862c4f5975abaef1ea4d4b0a","tid":316752,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"點解唔將全香港劃做內地管轄區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf69e83d0d1e888fc2fae9db8c3f9795f54f61cc","tid":316752,"uid":41821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"